{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 后效大盘分布分析 —— 消耗类\n",
    "\n",
    "**数据来源**：`ad_callback_log_from_ad_log_full`，通过 Spark 直连 Hive 取数  \n",
    "**分析维度**：`visitor_id`  \n",
    "**分箱方式**：首尾各1个尾部开区间（p5以下 / p95以上），中间8个等距分箱，共10箱  \n",
    "**覆盖口径**：总消耗 / 正常流量消耗 / 作弊流量消耗 / 内循环消耗 / 外循环CID消耗 / 线索消耗 / 下载消耗\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "**表结构说明**：\n",
    "- 同一个 `llsid`（一次广告曝光/点击）会产生多行记录\n",
    "  - **计费行**：`action_type = charge_action_type`，有 `cost_total`，用于消耗类分析\n",
    "  - **事件行**：`action_type` 为各种 `EVENT_*`，`cost_total = 0`，用于后效事件类分析\n",
    "- 本 notebook 只处理消耗类，Hive 层直接过滤 `action_type = charge_action_type` 取计费行"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 1：配置"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import warnings\n",
    "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n",
    "\n",
    "from pyspark.sql import SparkSession\n",
    "\n",
    "P_DATE = '20250101'\n",
    "N_BINS = 10\n",
    "\n",
    "INCYCLE_OCPC_TYPES     = \"'AD_MERCHANT_ROAS','EVENT_ORDER_PAIED','AD_STOREWIDE_ROAS','AD_MERCHANT_T7_ROI','AD_FANS_TOP_ROI'\"\n",
    "EXCYCLE_CID_OCPC_TYPES = \"'EVENT_ORDER_SUBMIT','AD_CID_ROAS','CID_ROAS','CID_EVENT_ORDER_PAID'\"\n",
    "CLUE_OCPC_TYPES        = \"'AD_LANDING_PAGE_FORM_SUBMITTED','EVENT_VALID_CLUES','AD_EFFECTIVE_CUSTOMER_ACQUISITION','EVENT_INTENTION_CONFIRMED','LEADS_SUBMIT','EVENT_PHONE_GET_THROUGH'\"\n",
    "DOWNLOAD_OCPC_TYPES    = \"'AD_CONVERSION','AD_PURCHASE','AD_PURCHASE_CONVERSION','AD_ROAS','AD_SEVEN_DAY_ROAS','AD_ITEM_DOWNLOAD_COMPLETED','AD_ITEM_CLICK_DOWNLOAD'\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 2：初始化 Spark"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "spark = SparkSession.builder.appName(\"cost_distribution_analysis\").enableHiveSupport().getOrCreate()\n",
    "print(\"Spark 初始化完成\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 3：从 Hive 取计费行并聚合到 visitor_id 维度\n",
    "\n",
    "在 Hive 层直接做 `GROUP BY visitor_id`，只拉聚合结果到 pandas，避免全量数据落本地。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "sql_cost = f\"\"\"\n",
    "SELECT\n",
    "    visitor_id,\n",
    "    SUM(cost_total) / 1000.0                                                                          AS total_cost_yuan,\n",
    "    SUM(IF(is_for_report_engine = true,  cost_total, 0)) / 1000.0                                     AS normal_cost_yuan,\n",
    "    SUM(IF(is_for_report_engine = false, cost_total, 0)) / 1000.0                                     AS spam_cost_yuan,\n",
    "    SUM(IF(ocpc_action_type IN ({INCYCLE_OCPC_TYPES}),     cost_total, 0)) / 1000.0                   AS incycle_cost_yuan,\n",
    "    SUM(IF(ocpc_action_type IN ({EXCYCLE_CID_OCPC_TYPES}), cost_total, 0)) / 1000.0                   AS excycle_cid_cost_yuan,\n",
    "    SUM(IF(ocpc_action_type IN ({CLUE_OCPC_TYPES}),        cost_total, 0)) / 1000.0                   AS clue_cost_yuan,\n",
    "    SUM(IF(ocpc_action_type IN ({DOWNLOAD_OCPC_TYPES}),    cost_total, 0)) / 1000.0                   AS download_cost_yuan\n",
    "FROM ks_origin_ad_log.ad_callback_log_from_ad_log_full\n",
    "WHERE p_date = '{P_DATE}'\n",
    "  AND is_duplicate = false\n",
    "  AND is_retry = false\n",
    "  AND action_type = charge_action_type\n",
    "GROUP BY visitor_id\n",
    "\"\"\"\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"正在从 Hive 取数...\")\n",
    "df = spark.sql(sql_cost).toPandas()\n",
    "print(f\"取数完成，visitor_id 数: {len(df):,}\")\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 4：工具函数"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def tail_equal_width_distribution(df, value_col, n_mid=8):\n",
    "    """\n",
    "    分箱策略：\n",
    "      Bin 1      : (0,        p5]   左尾\n",
    "      Bin 2~n+1  : (p5, p95] 等距切 n_mid 刀\n",
    "      Bin n+2    : (p95,  +∞) 右尾\n",
    "    共 n_mid + 2 = 10 个箱\n",
    "    """\n",
    "    s = df[value_col].dropna()\n",
    "    s = s[s > 0]\n",
    "    if s.empty:\n",
    "        print(f\"  [WARN] {value_col}: 无有效数据\")\n",
    "        return pd.DataFrame()\n",
    "\n",
    "    p5  = s.quantile(0.05)\n",
    "    p95 = s.quantile(0.95)\n",
    "\n",
    "    mid_edges = np.linspace(p5, p95, n_mid + 1)\n",
    "    edges = np.concatenate([[0], mid_edges, [np.inf]])\n",
    "    edges = np.unique(edges)\n",
    "\n",
    "    labels = []\n",
    "    for i in range(len(edges) - 1):\n",
    "        lo, hi = edges[i], edges[i + 1]\n",
    "        lo_str = f'{lo:.4f}' if lo != 0 and lo != np.inf else ('0' if lo == 0 else '+∞')\n",
    "        hi_str = f'{hi:.4f}' if hi != np.inf else '+∞'\n",
    "        labels.append(f'({lo_str}, {hi_str}]')\n",
    "\n",
    "    bins = pd.cut(s, bins=edges, labels=labels, include_lowest=True, right=True)\n",
    "    result = (\n",
    "        s.groupby(bins, observed=True)\n",
    "        .agg(cnt='count', min_val='min', max_val='max', avg_val='mean', total_val='sum')\n",
    "        .reset_index()\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    result.columns = ['分箱区间', '用户数cnt', '最小值(元)', '最大值(元)', '均值(元)', '总消耗(元)']\n",
    "    result['占比%'] = (result['用户数cnt'] / result['用户数cnt'].sum() * 100).round(2)\n",
    "    result['p5边界'] = round(p5, 4)\n",
    "    result['p95边界'] = round(p95, 4)\n",
    "    return result\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def show_distribution(result, metric_name, save_csv=True):\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n{'='*70}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  {metric_name}  （visitor_id维度，尾部开区间+中间等距，共10箱）\")\n",
    "    print(f\"{'='*70}\")\n",
    "    if result.empty:\n",
    "        return\n",
    "    print(result.to_string(index=False))\n",
    "    if save_csv:\n",
    "        fname = f\"dist_{metric_name}.csv\"\n",
    "        result.to_csv(fname, index=False)\n",
    "        print(f\"  => 已保存: {fname}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 5：各消耗口径分布分析"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 5.1 总消耗（total_cost_yuan）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "show_distribution(tail_equal_width_distribution(df, 'total_cost_yuan'), 'total_cost_yuan')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 5.2 正常流量消耗（normal_cost_yuan）\n",
    "> `is_for_report_engine = true`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "show_distribution(tail_equal_width_distribution(df, 'normal_cost_yuan'), 'normal_cost_yuan')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 5.3 作弊流量消耗（spam_cost_yuan）\n",
    "> `is_for_report_engine = false`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "show_distribution(tail_equal_width_distribution(df, 'spam_cost_yuan'), 'spam_cost_yuan')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 5.4 内循环消耗（incycle_cost_yuan）\n",
    "> `ocpc_action_type IN ('AD_MERCHANT_ROAS','EVENT_ORDER_PAIED','AD_STOREWIDE_ROAS','AD_MERCHANT_T7_ROI','AD_FANS_TOP_ROI')`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "show_distribution(tail_equal_width_distribution(df, 'incycle_cost_yuan'), 'incycle_cost_yuan')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 5.5 外循环CID消耗（excycle_cid_cost_yuan）\n",
    "> `ocpc_action_type IN ('EVENT_ORDER_SUBMIT','AD_CID_ROAS','CID_ROAS','CID_EVENT_ORDER_PAID')`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "show_distribution(tail_equal_width_distribution(df, 'excycle_cid_cost_yuan'), 'excycle_cid_cost_yuan')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 5.6 线索消耗（clue_cost_yuan）\n",
    "> `ocpc_action_type IN ('AD_LANDING_PAGE_FORM_SUBMITTED','EVENT_VALID_CLUES','AD_EFFECTIVE_CUSTOMER_ACQUISITION','EVENT_INTENTION_CONFIRMED','LEADS_SUBMIT','EVENT_PHONE_GET_THROUGH')`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "show_distribution(tail_equal_width_distribution(df, 'clue_cost_yuan'), 'clue_cost_yuan')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 5.7 下载消耗（download_cost_yuan）\n",
    "> `ocpc_action_type IN ('AD_CONVERSION','AD_PURCHASE','AD_PURCHASE_CONVERSION','AD_ROAS','AD_SEVEN_DAY_ROAS','AD_ITEM_DOWNLOAD_COMPLETED','AD_ITEM_CLICK_DOWNLOAD')`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "show_distribution(tail_equal_width_distribution(df, 'download_cost_yuan'), 'download_cost_yuan')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 6：汇总总览（p50 / p90 / p99）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "cost_cols = [\n",
    "    'total_cost_yuan', 'normal_cost_yuan', 'spam_cost_yuan',\n",
    "    'incycle_cost_yuan', 'excycle_cid_cost_yuan', 'clue_cost_yuan', 'download_cost_yuan'\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "summary = []\n",
    "for col in cost_cols:\n",
    "    s = df[col].dropna()\n",
    "    s = s[s > 0]\n",
    "    if s.empty:\n",
    "        summary.append({'口径': col, '有效UV数': 0})\n",
    "        continue\n",
    "    summary.append({\n",
    "        '口径': col,\n",
    "        '有效UV数': len(s),\n",
    "        '总消耗(元)': round(s.sum(), 2),\n",
    "        '人均消耗(元)': round(s.mean(), 4),\n",
    "        'p50': round(s.quantile(0.5), 4),\n",
    "        'p90': round(s.quantile(0.9), 4),\n",
    "        'p99': round(s.quantile(0.99), 4),\n",
    "    })\n",
    "\n",
    "summary_df = pd.DataFrame(summary)\n",
    "print(summary_df.to_string(index=False))\n",
    "summary_df.to_csv('cost_summary.csv', index=False)\n",
    "print(\"\\n=> 已保存: cost_summary.csv\")"
   ]
  }
